about.name: HOT ALOHA Niskin Bottles
about.description: Monthly measurements of the thermohaline structure, water column chemistry, and primary production were collected at station ALOHA as part of the HOT program.

about.name: CARIACO Niskin Bottles
about.description: Monthly measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations, and for productivity, phytoplankton, and pigment observations at station CARIACO.

about.name: KNOT Niskin Bottles
about.description: Irregular quasi-seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at station KNOT.

about.name: K2 Niskin Bottles
about.description: Irregular quasi-seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at station K2.

about.name: CVOO Niskin Bottles
about.description: Irregular quasi-seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at station CVOO.

about.name: Munida Niskin Bottles
about.description: Bi-monthly measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the deep station of the Munida transect.

about.name: RADCO Niskin Bottles
about.description: Monthly measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the RADCO stations near A Coruna as part of the RADIALES program.

about.name: GIFT Niskin Bottles
about.description: Seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the GIFT transect.

about.name: DYFAMED Niskin Bottles
about.description: Monthly measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the DYFAMED station.

about.name: IrmingerSea Time-Series Niskin Bottles
about.description: Seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the IrmingerSea time-series station.

about.name: IcelandSea Time-Series Niskin Bottles
about.description: Seasonal measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at the IcelandSea time-series station.

about.name: OWSM Niskin Bottles
about.description: Monthly measurements of CTD and in-situ Niskin-bottles samples for chemical observations at OWSM.

variableMeasured.name: TimeSeriesSite
variableMeasured.description: List abbrevations (or names) of the time-series stations.

variableMeasured.name: CRUISE
variableMeasured.description: Cruise identifier for cruise of particular station visit. Not consistently defined across the time-series stations.

variableMeasured.name: STNNBR
variableMeasured.description: Station identifier; a unique number or alphanumeric string designating a general geographic location at which one or more sampling activities may occur. Artficially created if not assigned by time-series station.

variableMeasured.name: CASTNO
variableMeasured.description: Numeric cast (profile) number of sample.

variableMeasured.name: BTLNBR
variableMeasured.description: Bottle number of sample.

variableMeasured.name: DATE
variableMeasured.description: Date of sample in yyyymmdd.

variableMeasured.name: TIME
variableMeasured.description: Time of sampling (utc, hhmm).

variableMeasured.name: LATITUDE
variableMeasured.description: Latitude where water samples were collected; north is positive. Latitude is a geographic coordinate which refers to the angle from a point on the Earth's surface to the equatorial plane

variableMeasured.name: LONGITUDE
variableMeasured.description: Longitude where water samples were collected; east is positive.

variableMeasured.name: CTDPRS
variableMeasured.description: Water pressure at measurement; depth reported as pressure; positive number increasing with water depth.

variableMeasured.name: SIGMA0
variableMeasured.description: Potential Density at 0dbar of sample.

variableMeasured.name: CTDTMP
variableMeasured.description: The degree of hotness at any position within a volume of fresh or salt water expressed against the International Temperature Scale 1990 (ITS-90) calibration standard.

variableMeasured.name: CTDSAL
variableMeasured.description: CTD Salinity on PSS-78 scale

variableMeasured.name: CTDSAL_FLAG_W
variableMeasured.description: WOCE quality flag of CTDSAL.

variableMeasured.name: CTDOXY
variableMeasured.description: CTD Oxygen

variableMeasured.name: CTDOXY_FLAG_W
variableMeasured.description: WOCE quality flag of CTDOXY.

variableMeasured.name: SALNTY
variableMeasured.description: Bottle salinity of sample.

variableMeasured.name: SALNTY_FLAG_W
variableMeasured.description: WOCE quality flag of bottle salinity.

variableMeasured.name: SALNTY_BPf
variableMeasured.description: Best-Pratice flag of bottle salinity.

variableMeasured.name: SALNTY_P
variableMeasured.description: Precision of bottle salinity based on replicate measurements.

variableMeasured.name: SALNTY_A
variableMeasured.description: Accuracy of bottle salinity based on CRM measurements.

variableMeasured.name: OXYGEN
variableMeasured.description: Bottle oxygen concentration (Winkler) of sample.

variableMeasured.name: OXYGEN_FLAG_W
variableMeasured.description: WOCE quality flag of bottle oxygen.

variableMeasured.name: OXYGEN_BPf
variableMeasured.description: Best-Pratice flag of bottle oxygen.

variableMeasured.name: OXYGEN_P
variableMeasured.description: Precision of bottle oxygen based on replicate measurements.

variableMeasured.name: OXYGEN_A
variableMeasured.description: Accuracy of bottle oxygen based on CRM measurements.

variableMeasured.name: NITRAT
variableMeasured.description: Nitrate concentration per mass seawater

variableMeasured.name: NITRAT_FLAG_W
variableMeasured.description: Nitrate quality flag; based on a PI established code; identifies a problem/quality issue with sample(s) from a given water bottle or single observation

variableMeasured.name: NITRAT_BPf
variableMeasured.description: Nitrate Best-Practice Flag: Indicates the extent to which Best-Practices have been followed (Lange et al. 2023).

variableMeasured.name: NITRAT_A
variableMeasured.description: Nitrate accuracy based on comparisons to reference material.

variableMeasured.name: NITRAT_P
variableMeasured.description: Nitrate precision based on replicate measurements.
